    "Body": " Head of Communications at AVA New York, NY ?? About the Job We are looking for someone to take on the Head of Communications role to garner interest in the COMPANY Platform and to continuously building a stronger COMPANY community. This person will play a critical role in designing and executing public relation strategies, ranging from approaches to conferences/meetups, leading social media channels, developing the community, and many more. Head of Communications responsibilities are: Create thought leadership strategy Maintain an understanding of trends within the blockchain industry affecting the COMPANY Platform and COMPANY Labs Develop and help nurture relationships with thought leaders and influencers to grow the product and industry awareness Spearhead opportunities to garner positive media and make COMPANY standout amongst the alternative blockchains Design and build out the communications team (i.e. social media manager, global community manager, etc.) Head of Communication requirements are: At least 5 years of experience as a marketing manager for a major brand in either traditional or blockchain companies You have a four-year degree in marketing, communications, or similar You have a deep understanding of how virality happens You understand how to tailor strategies for different social channels, and can execute all of them Passion for building and maintaining relationships Entrepreneurial spirit Experience with building and managing teams ", 
